org.epics.graphene

Interface AxisRangeInstance


  • public interface AxisRangeInstance
    A stateful object that computes the value range for a particular graph. It includes the state to compute the range for a particular axis on a particular graph.

    Objects of this type are mutable, and cannot be shared across different graphs, on different threads.

    Author:
    carcassi
